data.description:
Hurry! Come Look at this Charming, Affordable, Move-In-Ready Home! 
This home is located in a highly sought after ''Hoover Lake and Park'' Subdivision in Rankin County, Florence, MS. Residents enjoy awesome Amenities i.e., Fishing, Boating and Swimming in any of the 11 available lakes, Fun Seasonal Community Activities and use of the Pavilion, by the Swim Lake, for Special Gatherings. The beautiful White Log Cabin exterior of the home gives it a Dream Vacation Home feel, all year long! This home sits on a Peaceful Corner Lot that has great Curb Appeal. The Interior of the home Boasts an Open Floor Plan and just outside of the Kitchen, there is a Huge Covered Wooden Deck, which provides a fun place to mingle with friends and family. There are also Two Storage Buildings Next to the Home. Also, the new home owner can enjoy the extra vacant ''lot 20'' adjacent to the home for the Privacy!!
